{"tid":493061,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"中招沒？iPhone X現“天冷死機門” 蘋果不淡定了","createTime":"2017-12-08T07:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T06:11:31.000Z","uid":141060,"like":56,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"d50754826a747e77494af3cb9b3807a37d1874af","tid":493061,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:06:16.000Z","msg":"隨著冬天的到來，越來越多地方的氣溫也是低了起來，這對於iPhone X來說，絕對不是好消息。<br />\n據外媒報道稱，不少iPhone X用戶開始反饋，自己的手機在溫度低的地方開始無緣無故的死機，很是煩人。這個問題也引起了蘋果的重視。<br />\n報道中提到，目前蘋果正在調查iPhone X低溫死機事件，而手機的柔性印刷電路板供應商是韓國的Interflex，會是這件事情的主因，目前他們已經停產以配合蘋果的調查。<br />\n據悉，Interflex為iPhone X供應印刷電路板，芯片與顯示屏等各種零部件都在這裡連接在一起，而iPhone X的OLED屏幕有時會出現無反應或反應不准確的問題，基本都是電路板問題造成。<br />\n蘋果還沒有宣布最終解決的辦法，而這些遇到iPhone X天冷就死機問題的用戶，只能在溫度相對高的地方使用手機了，很尷尬是吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/150603_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F150603_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=a6fab30a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782eea1244eff02139babe802f433bc692b123b2","tid":493061,"uid":141060,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:07:15.000Z","msg":"可以順手開發埋發燒保護套 同急速加熱版ios<br />\n添曲又賺多筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264b22a8059e3c5ddd66091faaa353b3ca2ea047","tid":493061,"uid":281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:12:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd53e0e2800f3db9e9ec5a05e0aa066260cb84ad","tid":493061,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:16:57.000Z","msg":"即係上個月呢單嘢?<br />\n好似已經Fix埋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/amitchowdhry/2017/11/10/iphone-x-cold-environment/#12159e3c1f23\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Famitchowdh